{"type": "article", "id": 29971, "title": "定制化手提包", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-21T23:01:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160722003657PCEqlaLRQtNX71Bs.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>在卖手提包这件事上，纽约品牌 <a href=\"http://ansoncalder.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Anson Calder</a> 走的是不常见的定制化路线：在选择了手提包的款式之后，顾客可以从一系列为特定物品量身定制的配件中进行挑选，通过包内六条固定带将它们像口袋一样和手提包“缝合”起来，打造出独一无二的收纳空间。丰富的配件选择是这套定制系统的一大特色，除了手机壳、笔套等常用的小配件之外，雨伞袋、公文夹以及各尺寸的数码产品包应有尽有。无论是配件还是手提包都采用来自法国的小牛皮革精心打造，缝线则来自知名的德国品牌 Gutermann。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/59107441/anson-calder-bags-and-cases-customizable-access-w\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，单个手提包的价格为 560 美元，搭配四个配件后的价格为 940 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003749HDdaW0rfKxCRwBt9.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607220037461DLOUVcoXiRtNQKC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.447059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003746X0GCBSqiZtA97J3k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003746CxfzjYXruRdip8Il.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.989943\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}